txt.en: Broken palisades can be found in Limlók.\n\nYou should repair the broken palisades.
Yrsa Spearwife, wife of Runerik and chief warrior of Limlók, seeks to repair the broken palisades ruined by recent assaults upon the settlement.
Dead trees can be found in the Floodfells.\n\nYou should cut down dead trees and gather the wood.
'Runerik sees something useful in you that I do not.'

'Yes, I am Yrsa. Runerik sees something useful in you that I do not. He is a good warrior, a better thane, and an even greater husband. Do not cross him and do not cross me, understand?\n\n'Grr, fine. If Runerik asks you to assist us, I will still my tongue for now. Look around you... see the palisades in ruin? We need them repaired immediately. Find dead trees in the Floodfells. They will provide the wood to repair the palisades. Do not tell me when you are finished. I will know!'
